item.description: “Come join us in the celebration of Laura and Dennis' birthday (and any other April Babies). We will gather for some dinner and great conversation, then dance the night away with the band "Last Kid Picked" who is guaranteed to get you up and dancing” Edit
item.how_to_find_us: We will have a table reserved and a sign on the table or ask the host for Dennis or Laura's birthday party.
